geneVariantDescriptions.description: SSRP1 over exp indicates an over expression of the Ssrp1 protein. However, the mechanism causing the over expression is unspecified.

evidence.efficacyEvidence: In a preclinical study, CBL0137 treatment resulted in cell death in two human pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma cell lines over-expressing FACT complex (SSRP1 and SUPT16H) in culture and inhibited tumor growth in several PDX models (PMID: 25402820).

references.title: Curaxin CBL0137 eradicates drug resistant cancer stem cells and potentiates efficacy of gemcitabine in preclinical models of pancreatic cancer.

evidence.efficacyEvidence: In a preclinical study, the combination of CBL0137 and Gemzar (gemcitabine) synergized to inhibit cell growth in two human pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma cell lines over-expressing FACT complex (SSRP1 and SUPT16H) in culture and inhibited tumor growth in one cell line xenograft model and several PDX models (PMID: 25402820).
